title: UNSANITY-Window Shade OSX PPC-INTEL package
description:
UNSANITY-Window Shade OSX PPC-INTEL package

Here is a compilation and merger of the super Window Shade app
from Unsanity.

This was compiled from the PirateButter torrent which included only the Windowshade that will work with os x 10.6x. 
I added the last update for Mac users still using 10.4x - 10.5x.
Not sure if this works for 10.3x users!

TRANSLATION : THIS WILL WORK WITH MAC USERS USING
PPC, INTEL, OS 10.4x-10.6x !!!


Just follow the instructions inside : READ ME-INSTRUCTIONS-WindowShade X Registration Kit.rtf

This is one of those apps that should be included free inside all macs, since it was developed way back with the classic mac, but disabled in the 10.x software, which boggles the mind. 
This unfairness is what brings this app to Demonoid / Piratebay .
Kill stupidity
